  <num>2-423</num>
  <heading>Damages.</heading>
  <text>Upon a finding by the judge of unjust imprisonment in accordance with the standards set by <cite path="§2-422|(a)">§ 2-422(a)</cite>, the judge may award damages. Punitive damages may not be awarded.</text>
